{"tid":701921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消委會：中國製無牌子USB轉插觸電風險高 機電署籲立即停用","createTime":"2018-06-14T13:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T16:27:52.000Z","uid":54733,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"85fbf5d9f51eb15dced33ed97ad55d48960ab2d2","tid":701921,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jiEHT2RzqhyRMO3gIyhaEA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180614a094655.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjiEHT2RzqhyRMO3gIyhaEA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180614a094655.jpg&h=466c2d71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">中國製無牌子旅遊插蘇觸電風險高。消委會圖片</span><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】消委會測試了10款USB旅行萬能蘇，售價由＄78至＄460，全部型號皆屬活動式插腳，全部樣本均未能通過所有安全標準的測試項目，其中2款無牌子但在市場上常見的樣本，整體安全評分只有2分或以下，情況令人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n測試結果顯示中國製造的無牌子樣本的不同插腳可同時伸出並鎖緊，型號為「931D」，由於各插腳的有關導電體互相接通，當其中一組插腳插上電源，其餘任何外露的插腳都會帶電，增加用戶觸電的風險，其他樣本的設計都不容許多於一組的插腳在同一時間伸出，用戶若想在產品伸出另一組插腳，必先把原先已伸出的插腳收回，以減少插腳帶電互連及外露的機會。<br />\n<br />\n消委會會將是次測試結果交由機電工程署跟進，機電署其後呼籲消費者馬上停用測試型號「931D」及另外兩款設計上與「931D」相似的旅行萬能蘇。<br />\n<br />\n其餘9款均通過絕緣測試，帶電部分備有絕緣保護，不會被用戶觸摸到，觸電風險很低，該署現正與相關供應商跟進不符合標準的項目。<br />\n<br />\n評分最低的五款USB轉插<br />\n<br />\n●無牌子（中國製）<br />\n<br />\n型號：931D<br />\n<br />\n售價：＄78<br />\n<br />\n●無牌子（中國製）<br />\n<br />\n型號：Universal Travel Adaptor<br />\n<br />\n售價：＄98<br />\n<br />\n●Adam Elements（中國製）<br />\n<br />\n型號：TA502<br />\n<br />\n售價：＄269<br />\n<br />\n●ecDigi（中國製）<br />\n<br />\n型號：TA25<br />\n<br />\n售價：＄150<br />\n<br />\n●Verbatim（中國製）<br />\n<br />\n型號：5-port Travel Adaptor<br />\n<br />\n售價：＄229<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/消委會-國產無牌子usb轉插觸電風險高-機電署籲立即停用-020000382.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%A2%E7%84%A1%E7%89%8C%E5%AD%90usb%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%92%E8%A7%B8%E9%9B%BB%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E9%AB%98-%E6%A9%9F%E9%9B%BB%E7%BD%B2%E7%B1%B2%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8-020000382.html&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e4da837b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/消委會-國產無牌子usb轉插觸電風險高-機電署籲立即停用-020000382.html</a>"},{"pid":"e7f960d3a360d72aa388ba06c5acda06d0d6049e","tid":701921,"uid":44211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"工聯會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c3bcfd9dd74c4a5e52e336c9c1355599ba2fd2","tid":701921,"uid":54733,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e7f960d3a360d72aa388ba06c5acda06d0d6049e","tid":701921,"uid":44211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"工聯會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"工聯會萬能蘇贈品易致觸電<br />\n城大碩士生：想謀殺我阿婆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20151227/19428225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151227%2F19428225&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=75bc13f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151227%2F19428225&h=9352f81b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20151227/19428225</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a82d26d25d9c15020a70a0433f76f2a38272c9","tid":701921,"uid":9171,"lik